================================================================================

ATTRIBUTIONS

This automation framework was created by analyzing and automating the manual
installation procedures documented in the OpenShift installation guide for
Cloudera Data Services. The implementation follows Red Hat's official
documentation and uses their provided CloudFormation templates as reference.

Key contributors and sources:
- Red Hat OpenShift documentation team
- OpenShift installer project contributors
- AWS CloudFormation template authors
- Terraform AWS provider maintainers
- Cloudera Professional Services documentation

