REQUIRED LICENSES AND SUBSCRIPTIONS

Users of this software must obtain appropriate licenses and subscriptions:

1. RED HAT SUBSCRIPTIONS
   - Valid Red Hat OpenShift Container Platform subscription
   - Required for production use
   - Available at: https://www.redhat.com/en/technologies/cloud-computing/openshift

2. CLOUDERA LICENSES
   - Valid Cloudera Data Services license (if using Cloudera)
   - Required for Cloudera workloads
   - Available at: https://www.cloudera.com/

3. AWS ACCOUNT
   - Active AWS account
   - Acceptance of AWS terms of service
   - Sign up at: https://aws.amazon.com/

